<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5> charge something down to someone • charge something up to someone</xh5><p> <i>charge something down to someone</i>—<i>(also: put something down to someone)</i> record a sum of money as a person’s debt for later payment: Please <u>charge these goods down to</u> my account.</p><p> <i>charge something up to someone</i>—(also: charge something upon someone) = charge something down to someone: Why were the expenses of the reception <u>charged up to</u> me?</p> </entry>
